_PAGE_UTILS_A_SORT_BY_DESCRIPTION_: Extends lodash's sortBy with case-insensitive comparison by default while keeping support for every iteratee shorthand.
_PAGE_UTILS_A_SORT_BY_ARGUMENTS_COLLECTI: Collection to iterate over (array or object).
_PAGE_UTILS_A_SORT_BY_ARGUMENTS_ITERATEE: Iteratees that describe the sort criteria; accepts property paths, functions, arrays, or shorthand objects.
_PAGE_UTILS_A_SORT_BY_ARGUMENTS_OPTIONS_: Optional configuration object ({ caseSensitive?: boolean }) passed as the last argument.
